            <noteGrp type="workDesc">
               <note type="description">Strophic poem consisting of 5-line stanzas – a poetic
                     expansion of verses by Abū Madyan. See translation and study by Gerald Elmore:
                     ‘Ibn al-ʿArabī’s ‘Cinquain’ (Takhmīs) on a poem by Abū Madyan’ in Arabica Vol.
                     46, 1998, pp. 63-96.</note>
