            <!-- Stemmatics -->
            <note type="stemmatics">Only three mss. listed by OY. We have looked at two of them,
                  both late copies with no historical evidence to support attribution to IA. The
                  content, however, strongly favours the attribution. See translation and study by
                  Gerald Elmore in Arabica Vol. 46, 1998, pp. 63-96. Further work needed.</note>
